      label: "Read more",
    },
    image: imgIntroBioEpi,
    imageAlt: "Introduction to Biostatistics and Epidemiology course poster",
  },
  {
    title:
      "National Seminar on Tropical Biology in conjunction with Jogja MultiOmics Update",
    description: [
      "We were invited as speakers at a seminar organized by the Faculty of Biology at Gadjah Mada University on July 19, 2025. We shared updates on our study integrating individual genomic datasets to discover biomarkers for cervical pre-cancer, presented by Innas Widiasti, M.Biomed, our Bioinformatician. Her excellent delivery led to fruitful discussions, generating thought-provoking questions and valuable feedback from the audience. The seminar also provided an opportunity to connect with and learn from distinguished researchers, academics, and clinical practitioners about their latest research developments.",
    ],
