    description: [
      "One of our team members had the privilege of attending a conference organized by the Indonesian Ministry of Health, at Bali Nusa Dua Conference Center (3-5 October 2024). The event provided a valuable opportunity to explore potential research collaborations and gain insights from leading experts in the field. We extend our gratitude to Yayasan Satriabudi Dharma Setia for sponsoring this meaningful experience.",
    ],
